Class VideoObj

java.lang.Object
VideoObj
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable
final class VideoObj
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
Immutable Data Class for video objects. Comprises a triple: title, year, director.
